folder: Franklin Avenue & Quincy Street, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Franklin Avenue, at Quincy Street. View 1,2 show an old frame at the southwest corner of the intersection. View 3 shows the buildings adjoining the southeast corner. Note the old frame dwelling hemmed in between two apartment buildings.

August 30, 1941
Views 1-3

P. L. Sperr
